Author: FishyGuts#5085
Content:
Well we had a close comp for the voting.   
@wookie okie went the extra mile and recruited new people into crypto and pirate while trying to get his logo some votes.  
The P with the eyepatch had too many iterations or it would have swept first place I think, so @Ignacio Figueroa (FIG) , @Llama and @Hermes let's collaborate next time 😃  @Hoffenbrau came out of nowhere with a last minute submission to place.   
Here are the tallied results.

Author: FishyGuts#5085
Content:
After removing the votes Wookie had with no z addresses or other issues, he ended up with 11 votes too.   A shocking three way tie.   
So @wookie , @Ignacio Figueroa (FIG) , @Hermes  - DM me your Zaddresses!   @Llama and I just squared up.  I sent @Hoffenbrau a message since he has yet to frequent the discord.   He will though soon.

Author: FishyGuts#5085
Content:
We will use the Sabre and Eyepatch logos to represent the coin until we get an entire design deck completed for the project.   
We really appreciate all the hard work everyone put in and we don't want you to spend all your booty in one place....  Unless that place is Tortuga... then feel free to make it rain.

Content: So in essence, all these have helped to shape the future feel of pirate so again, thank you all.
